# Trivy suppression file.
#
# One entry per line. Formats:
#   CVE-2024-12345                       (silence a CVE globally)
#   CVE-2024-12345 exp:2026-01-01        (silence with expiry)
#   AVD-DS-0002                          (silence a misconfig rule id)
#
# Every entry should be justified in a comment. Prefer fixing over ignoring.
